<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>msẖtạq lk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- msẖtạq lk mn qlby msẖtạqlk yạrby
 msẖtạq trjʿly ạlfrḥh wmn nạrk tsẖʿl ḥby
 msẖtạq llạ̹kẖtbạrạt wḥyạẗ ạlạ̹ntṣạrạt
 msẖtạq ạ̉rjʿ ạ̉sẖhdlk wạmjạdk tmly̱ drby
 ạlqrạr- ḥbk ʿmrh mạ btgẖyr rby ạ̉kyd ạ̉nạ ltgẖyrt
 sẖkẖṣk ḥạḍr mstny lkn mn jhly tạ̉kẖrt
 ạlmạḍy wạlạ̉frạḥ mn gẖyrk kạnwạ jrạḥ
 lsh btsẖfy wbtʿwḍ ạ̉ktr bktyr mn l rạḥ
 2- msẖtạq ạ̉nạ ạḥkylk ʿn nfsy w ạ̉sẖkylk
 msẖtạq ạ̉smʿlk wạkẖḍlʿk wmn qlby ạ̉gẖnylk
 tʿṭyny ạ̉srạrk wthdyny bạ̉fkạrk
 msẖtạq trjʿ tḥmlny tqwyny lmạ bjylk</lyrics>
<hymn_number>6538</hymn_number>
<author>ạ̹yạd ḥdạd, ạ̹yạd ḥdạd</author>
</song>